---
title: Honey Garlic Pork Meatballs with Hoisin Veg Noodles and Toasted Sesame Seeds
description: These Honey Garlic Pork Meatballs are a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
